comments: Curry (PHI) moves laterally defending Young's (ATL) drive and marginal contact occurs.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL) moves along with Curry (PHI) and engages with him, but does not initiate contact that causes him to fall to the floor.
Capela (ATL) places his hand to Embiid's (PHI) side and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Maxey's (PHI) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Young (ATL) delivers contact to Curry's (PHI) lower body and the contact dislodges him from his position.
Embiid (PHI) is already in Luwawu-Cabarrot's (ATL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Maxey (PHI) is already in Capela's (ATL) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Green (PHI) places his forearm to Young's (ATL) front during his drive to the basket and marginal contact occurs.
Young (ATL) establishes himself in a screening position in Embiid's (PHI) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Green (ATL) places his hand to Collins' (ATL) side at the end of his drive and the contact is marginal.
Maxey (PHI) establishes himself in a screening position in Collins' (ATL) path and makes marginal contact as they disengage.
Embiid (PHI) and Collins (ATL) engage in the post and the contact between the two players is marginal.
Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL) makes marginal contact to Green (PHI) and disengages as they pursue the loose ball.
Thybulle (PHI) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Embiid (PHI) briefly grasps Gallinari's (ATL) jersey but the marginal contact does not affect his SQBR or jump shot attempt.
